### parallel_read_url
Read multiple web pages in parallel (max 5 URLs).

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| urls | array | Yes | - | URL configs with url, withAllLinks, withAllImages |
| timeout | number | No | 30000 | Timeout in milliseconds |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "Jina AI", toolName: "parallel_read_url", arguments: { urls: [{ url: "https://example.com" }], timeout: 30000 } })

